{"tid":1844272,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特區政府限制湖北省居民同過去14日去過湖北嘅人入香港","createTime":"2020-01-26T14:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T15:05:04.000Z","uid":50386,"like":7,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"3ac11ae0b2fe4b9eafe2a414063a6622bc2e450e","tid":1844272,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GeQw4Uh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGeQw4Uh.png&h=359f44dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5382af23d8593b3bd8965caaffae85b2817e18ac","tid":1844272,"uid":258731,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ABcOV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ABcOV7.jpg&h=0f21f561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鑑於中國肺炎疫症嚴峻，港共政府倒行逆施，徹底失去民意信任，已經無力領導現今疫症。<br />\n加上此疫症已經在香港鄰近地區面臨失控下，有機會令香港國家陷入危機，影響香港國家存亡。<br />\n<br />\n為防止中國肺炎在香港大規模爆發，在此宣佈，於香港時間2020年1月26日21時30分正式頒布緊急狀態令<br />\n為免錯過對抗中國肺炎黃金機會，全體連登網民會即時接管香港權力，全力帶領香港國民對抗中國肺炎，以 香港國民福祉為依歸。<br />\n請各位緊記，香港國家一切權力屬於人民，港共政權並非必然行使權力者。<br />\n<br />\n所有重大事件及決策，將會於連登討論區「政事台」討論及表決<br />\n議案帖文將會以【議案】為首以作識別<br />\n<br />\n大多數民意支持，以及正評數量淨值為1000或以上， 該議案會被視作「獲得通過」<br />\n<br />\n正式實現全民參政，全民議政<br />\n議案通過後，將運用全體公民力量及權力，以及民間一切可能的方法實行各種政策 。<br />\n請各位再次緊記，港共政權並非必然行使權力者，權力永遠歸於所有香港國民。<br />\n<br />\n【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844124</a>"},{"pid":"e0cc12c61ff5a76459b6507585924ec73130c8e6","tid":1844272,"uid":76341,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:34:51.000Z","msg":"計好數第15日即刻落黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b430b025a223242755de5cce6109157b3d3c745b","tid":1844272,"uid":10398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:34:52.000Z","msg":"淨係湖北<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9023abcbc1b8e7bd9a1c9783037ed2d75fc276b3","tid":1844272,"uid":176567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:35:11.000Z","msg":"淨係湖北？？？"},{"pid":"2cdabd7b28ef348b7064adf1b4f0605af1e0ad9d","tid":1844272,"uid":282925,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:35:24.000Z","msg":"其他省都好撚嚴重囉戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40077df5254d95d67dc5f8b63827b819f646ed9c","tid":1844272,"uid":128959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:35:29.000Z","msg":"硬係要自己大大力打巴自己"},{"pid":"94f2e4e5e1b49194d5f626c4d0b1363106e4e812","tid":1844272,"uid":65888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"又暫緩？"},{"pid":"b1c317ad7e89742db8c4d0a5919a7fd7b7469458","tid":1844272,"uid":6752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:35:38.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩,佢話唔係湖北你撚知"},{"pid":"313de09c18a58fd90fcf03ca5e227e0a18f89887","tid":1844272,"uid":282925,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:35:53.000Z","msg":"永遠訴求都係做一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88775c4b9d7e5023fff5bb6490abfe3233bc65b6","tid":1844272,"uid":70507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:35:53.000Z","msg":"唔罷工唔肯做野"},{"pid":"ce3e8f1b8c5e959fef79b7cdb3ccfd3fb8318fd7","tid":1844272,"uid":19842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:36:00.000Z","msg":"班支那狗入境個陣乜柒都唔報有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on9 玩撚完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35141b97cbedd810676aaf4ea21f194d5740acb1","tid":1844272,"uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:36:06.000Z","msg":"習帝終於有時間批香港奏摺啦